主党的选情有太大影响。」他说道。 《每日经济新闻》记者注意到，躲过暗杀后，特朗普在美国政治赌博网站 PredictIt 上的赢面瞬时大涨，被称为「特朗普交易」之一的比特币亦在 14 日升破 6 万美元。特朗普宾州拉票遇袭，胜选概率升至 71%，马斯克等大佬表态！专家解读：美国大选已演变成政治暴力"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9923637b64fea6cfa8b6d273635469d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661639589"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIiYCrw4fE+MZdEAMaCTEwOTMwODgxMSCZ5tG0BjAAOPoCQBNyCTY2MTYzOTU4OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1721047139.769846", "card_id": "Q_661641778", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "家用咖啡机和咖啡店的咖啡味道差别在哪里？有好用的家用款推荐吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在咖啡店的咖啡备受欢迎的情况下，在家自制咖啡成为越来越多人的新选择。这不禁让人好奇：家用咖啡机做出的咖啡和咖啡店的咖啡，味道到底有没有差别呢？设备的专业程度会不会让奶泡的细腻程度、咖啡的醇厚口感有所区别？是咖啡店的专业咖啡师赋予了咖啡独特的灵魂，还是家用咖啡机在便捷性中丢失了某些关键的味道元素？如果想买家用款的话，应该推荐哪款呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8202ac26d855f161a8e4d2844bf65774_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661641778"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IiYCrw4fE+MZdEAMaCTEwOTMwOTI4NCCS+dG0BjAAOEtAFHIJNjYxNjQxNzc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1721047139.770242", "card_id": "Q_661621658", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 欧洲杯决赛西班牙夺得冠军，你如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ed5ea19b0a30b4ab31af520f451a783_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link"